Product Description
DRAGON WARRIOR VII: PRIMA&#039;S OFFICIAL STRATEGY GUIDE invites you to join in the best-selling RPG adventure from Enix, DRAGON WARRIOR VII. Prima offers gamers a complete step-by-step walkthrough including hidden side-quests, detailed character info and stats, and hot tips on how to take advantage of all items in every enchanted area. You&#039;ll also get info about every monster and tips on minigames and medals. Here&#039;s your chance to be a hero and restore the world to its former glory!

* Step-by-step walkthroughs of every town, tower, cave, dungeon, castle, and hidden quest
* Detailed maps of all areas
* Vital stats of all spells, weaponry, and items
* Locations of all puzzle shards and medals
* Strategies for winning all minigames
* Complete Bestiary of all monsters
